- **Policy Number:** EXT-2025-001----## Introduction
Extendicare (Canada) Inc. is committed to providing information in an accessible format or with communication supports to people with disabilities, taking into account their specific needs.## Important Note
This document is uncontrolled when printed.## Contact Information
For any inquiries, please place an order through our Print Shop: Extendicare Print Shop## Confidentiality Statement
Confidential and Proprietary Information of Extendicare (Canada) Inc. Â© 2025----## Accessibility Commitment

- Requests for accessible formats can be made through the designated contact channels.----## Conclusion
For further assistance or to request information in an accessible format, please reach out to our support team.----**Page 1 of 1**
